        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At <strong>Insuranex</strong>, our mission is to revolutionize the insurance industry by providing cutting-edge technology solutions that empower insurance agents, enhance customer experiences, and streamline policy management.</p>
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p><strong>Insuranex</strong> is a dynamic team of passionate professionals with expertise in insurance, software development, and user experience design. Our diverse backgrounds allow us to approach challenges from different angles, ensuring that our platform meets the needs of both agents and clients.</p>
